All Classes and Interfaces

Class
Description
AbstractObservableField
Abstract class implementing Observable interface operations.
CommonField
Interface to the fields that can be placed on the board maze Maze.
CommonField.Direction
Enumeration type that defines the direction of movement in the maze.
CommonMaze
Interface representing a game (maze) that works with CommonMazeObject objects and CommonField fields.
CommonMazeObject
CommonMazeObject interface represents common object in maze
ComponentView
The ComponentView interface represents objects that can be placed under a FieldView.
FieldView
FieldView class represents the view for displaying the field in a graphical user interface.
GameMain
The GameMain class is the entry point of the game application.
GameOverContent
GameOverContent class display a game over screen in a game.
GhostObject
GhostObject class represents ghost object in maze
GhostView
The GhostView class represents the graphical view of a ghost component.
KeyObject
KeyObject class represents key object in maze
KeyView
The KeyView class represents the graphical view of a key component.
MazeConfigure
MazeConfigure class represents maze configuration from file, also it can load maze from file and interpret it.
MazePlan
MazePlan class represents maze plan
MazePresenter
MazePresenter class display a game screen with maze and other attributes.
MazeSelection
MazeSelection class display a screen where player can choose maze for a game.
MenuPresenter
MenuPresenter class display a menu screen in a game.
MessageDialog
MessageDialog class display a message screen in a game when player chose wrong combination of buttons in logging settings.
MyKeyListener
The MyKeyListener class implements the KeyListener interface to handle press on the buttons 'w', 's', 'd', 'a'.
Observable
An Observable interface representing objects that can notify dependent objects (observers) of changes. you can insert Mazeobjects.
Observable.Observer
Observer interface for objects that need to be notified of changes in observable objects.
PacmanGame
The PacmanGame class represents the Pacman game.
PacmanObject
PacmanObject class represents pacman object in maze
PacmanView
The PacmanView class represents the graphical view of a pacman component.
PathField
PathField class represents path field in maze
PointObject
PointObject class represents point object in maze
PointView
The PointView class represents the graphical view of a point component.
SettingPresenter
SettingPresenter class display a settings screen for a load of the game.
TargetField
TargetField class represents target object in maze
WallField
WallField class represents wall object in maze
